Fam_a_ lakum fee almun_a_fiqeena fi-atayni wa*A*ll_a_hu arkasahum bim_a_ kasaboo atureedoona an tahdoo man a_d_alla All_a_hu waman yu_d_lili All_a_hu falan tajida lahu sabeel_a_*n*
Waddoo law takfuroona kam_a_ kafaroo fatakoonoona saw_a_an fal_a_ tattakhi_th_oo minhum awliy_a_a _h_att_a_ yuh_a_jiroo fee sabeeli All_a_hi fa-in tawallaw fakhu_th_oohum wa*o*qtuloohum _h_aythu wajadtumoohum wal_a_ tattakhi_th_oo minhum waliyyan wal_a_ na_s_eer_a_*n*
