Inna alla_th_eena tawaff_a_humu almal_a_-ikatu \_th_\_a_limee anfusihim q_a_loo feema kuntum q_a_loo kunn_a_ musta_d_AAafeena fee al-ar_d_i q_a_loo alam takun ar_d_u All_a_hi w_a_siAAatan fatuh_a_jiroo feeh_a_ faol_a_-ika ma\w_a_hum jahannamu was_a_at ma_s_eer_a_*n*
